snippet.title: This Piano Speaks English
snippet.description:
Oh, and it can also play the world's hardest song... sort of.  Visit https://brilliant.org/markrober to sign up for free. The first 2000 people will get 20% off their annual premium membership.

Shout out to Sheet Music Boss. Go check out and sub to their channel!- https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzTR9iSH-TFC4-ocDS_ll4A

Also go check out Grant from 3Blue1Brown. He the best explainer of complicated stuff I know (the buttery smooth delivery certainly doesn‚Äôt hurt)- https://www.3blue1brown.com/

Finally, the piano in the video is from Edelweiss. We had to modify it so it could play Rush E and all the keys at once otherwise out of the box they can play about 30 keys at once.  If you want more info, you can find it here- https://www.edelweissinfo.com/

P.S. No Chopstix were hurt in the filming of this video (i.e. he didn‚Äôt ACTUALLY catch fire).  I took some creative liberty in the form of a smoke bomb :)
